## Integration with Daily Content

### After Generating Theory

```bash
# After completing /create-day for Day XX

# Generate corresponding CFD lab
/create-lab --day=XX --type=cfd

# Generate C++ lab if new concept introduced
/create-lab --day=XX --type=cpp
```

### Spaced Repetition Schedule

```
Day 01: Theory (Governing Equations)
Day 02: Theory (Finite Volume Method)
Day 03: Lab 01 (Continuity implementation) ← Spaced practice
Day 04: Theory (Spatial Discretization)
Day 05: Lab 02 (FVM implementation) ← Spaced practice
...
```

