## C++ Learning Track (16 Modules)

| Module | Topics | OpenFOAM Examples |
|--------|--------|-------------------|
| **cpp_01_basics** | Types, operators, control flow | `dimensionedScalar`, field indexing |
| **cpp_02_functions** | Functions, parameters, return types | `fvm::ddt()`, `fvc::div()` |
| **cpp_03_oop** | Classes, constructors, destructors | `fvMesh`, `volScalarField` |
| **cpp_04_inheritance** | Base/derived, virtual functions | `surfaceInterpolationScheme` hierarchy |
| **cpp_05_polymorphism** | Virtual dispatch, abstract classes | `limiter()` virtual methods |
| **cpp_06_operators** | Operator overloading | `operator+`, `operator|=` for fields |
| **cpp_07_templates** | Function templates, class templates | `tmp<T>`, `Field<Type>` |
| **cpp_08_stl** | Containers, algorithms, iterators | OpenFOAM vs STL comparison |
| **cpp_09_memory** | Smart pointers, RAII | `autoPtr`, `refPtr`, `tmp` |
| **cpp_10_move** | Move semantics, perfect forwarding | `std::move()`, `auto(T&&)` |
| **cpp_11_constexpr** | Compile-time computation | `dimensionSet` compile-time checks |
| **cpp_12_concepts** | C++20 concepts | Template constraints |
| **cpp_13_dsa_arrays** | Sparse arrays, compressed storage | `UILList`, `LduMatrix` |
| **cpp_14_dsa_graphs** | Mesh as graph, adjacency | Cell-face connectivity |
| **cpp_15_dsa_trees** | Octree, cell tree | `cellTree`, `boundBox` |
| **cpp_16_algorithms** | Iterative solvers, CG, BiCGStab | `PCG`, `PBiCGStab` |

