## Troubleshooting

### Lab Generation Fails

```bash
# Check ground truth was extracted
cat /tmp/lab_ground_truth_XX.json

# Check skeleton was created
cat labs/labXX_skeleton.json

# Check verification report
cat /tmp/lab_verification_XX.txt
```

### DeepSeek API Errors

```bash
# Test API connection
python3 .claude/scripts/deepseek_content.py deepseek-chat <(echo "test")

# Check API key
grep DEEPSEEK_API_KEY .mcp.json
```

### Lab Content Issues

```bash
# Re-run specific stage
# Stage 4: Regenerate content
python3 .claude/scripts/deepseek_content.py \
  deepseek-chat \
  /tmp/lab_stage4_prompt.txt \
  > daily_learning/Phase_XX/XX_lab.md
```

